; Coverage for amount.cc lines 204, 220:
; Standard comma thousands separator with period decimal in register output.
; The register command forces amount formatting through stream_out_mpq with
; the commodity parameter, hitting line 204 (decimal point) and line 220
; (thousands comma separator) for amounts with >3 integer digits.

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2024/01/01 Big Purchase
    Expenses:Goods         $54,321.99
    Assets:Bank

test reg Expenses
24-Jan-01 Big Purchase          Expenses:Goods           $54,321.99   $54,321.99
end test
